<section id="products" class="section bg-accent relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-primary">專為敏感毛孩設計的洗毛精</h2>
      <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
        每一瓶 Forest Calm 都是為了守護敏感毛孩而生，精心挑選天然成分，給予毛孩最溫柔的清潔體驗。
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Pure Calm Product -->
      <div class="card overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-white h-80">
          <img 
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5273044/pexels-photo-5273044.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600" 
            alt="Pure Calm 無香舒敏" 
            class="w-full h-full object-contain p-8 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-primary text-white py-1 px-3 rounded-full text-sm">
            無香配方
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl">Pure Calm 無香舒敏</h3>
            <span class="text-xl font-medium text-primary-dark">NT$550</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            專為極敏毛孩設計，主打無香、無刺激配方。米白瓶身搭配綠色瓶蓋，簡約純淨。
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
              </svg>
              500ml
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              極度敏感適用
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex space-x-3">
            <a href="/products/pure-calm" class="btn-outline flex-1 text-center">了解更多</a>
            <a href="/#sample" class="btn-primary flex-1 text-center">索取體驗包</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Forest Gentle Product -->
      <div class="card overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/20 to-white h-80">
          <img 
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6816304/pexels-photo-6816304.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600" 
            alt="Forest Gentle 森林香氛" 
            class="w-full h-full object-contain p-8 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-secondary text-white py-1 px-3 rounded-full text-sm">
            天然香氛
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl">Forest Gentle 森林香氛</h3>
            <span class="text-xl font-medium text-primary-dark">NT$550</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            添加天然精油，低敏森林香氛。深褐瓶身搭配黑色瓶蓋，展現自然氣息。
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center mr-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" />
              </svg>
              500ml
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary mr-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              輕度敏感適用
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex space-x-3">
            <a href="/products/forest-gentle" class="btn border-2 border-secondary text-secondary hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white flex-1 text-center">了解更多</a>
            <a href="/#sample" class="btn bg-secondary text-white hover:bg-secondary-light flex-1 text-center">索取體驗包</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute -right-16 top-1/3 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute left-0 bottom-0 w-full h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 to-secondary/5"></div>
</section>